This paper focuses on sentiment analysis on informal short texts using deep neural network models. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
